# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OVERCLOCK.EXE — Environment Variables
#
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Fill in your values
# 3. Never commit .env to source control
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SUPABASE (Required)
# Get these from: https://supabase.com/dashboard → Your Project → Settings → API
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Project URL
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co

# Anonymous/Public Key (safe to expose in frontend)
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ADMOB - Mobile Ads (Required for APK monetization)
# Get these from: https://admob.google.com → Apps → Ad Units
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Your AdMob App ID (found in App Settings)
VITE_ADMOB_APP_ID=ca-app-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX~XXXXXXXXXX

# Rewarded Ad Unit IDs (create separate units for each platform)
VITE_ADMOB_ANDROID_REWARDED_UNIT_ID=ca-app-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/XXXXXXXXXX
VITE_ADMOB_IOS_REWARDED_UNIT_ID=ca-app-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/XXXXXXXXXX

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CAPACITOR / ANDROID BUILD INFO
# (Configured in capacitor.config.ts - no env vars needed)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# App ID: com.overclock.exe
# App Name: OVERCLOCK.EXE
# Web Dir: dist

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# BUILD COMMANDS QUICK REFERENCE
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# FIRST TIME SETUP:
#   1. pnpm install
#   2. pnpm build
#   3. pnpm cap:add:android
#
# BUILD APK:
#   1. pnpm build:android
#   2. In Android Studio: Build → Build Bundle(s) / APK(s) → Build APK(s)
#   3. APK location: android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
#
# AFTER CODE CHANGES:
#   pnpm build:mobile
#
# REQUIREMENTS:
#   - Android Studio installed
#   - Android SDK installed
#   - Java JDK 17+
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
